title: I hope this Ahri skin isnt the "new" skin
body:
Didnt wait over a year to get a skin in a COMPLELTELY similar theme as Popstar(isnt it same theme even? just different cloth?)?

I hope its not her skin this year. Wanted something like bloodmoon :(

If not, i hope this new one is actually quite good and does have a fresh feeling when playing her.
